	determined by reading the
	<span class=3D"quote">=E2=80=9C<span class=3D"quote"><a class=3D"link" hre=
f=3D"https://www.nongnu.org/ext2-doc/ext2.html#bg-inode-bitmap" title=3D"bg=
_inode_bitmap">bg_inode_bitmap</a></span>=E2=80=9D</span>
	in its associated <a class=3D"link" href=3D"https://www.nongnu.org/ext2-do=
c/ext2.html#block-group-descriptor-table" title=3D"Block Group Descriptor T=
able">group descriptor</a>.
   </p><p>
