de-table" title=3D"bg_inode_table">bg_inode_table</a>
	in its associated <a class=3D"link" href=3D"https://www.nongnu.org/ext2-do=
c/ext2.html#block-group-descriptor-table" title=3D"Block Group Descriptor T=
able">group descriptor</a>.
	There are <a class=3D"link" href=3D"https://www.nongnu.org/ext2-doc/ext2.h=
tml#s-inodes-per-group" title=3D"s_inodes_per_group">s_inodes_per_group</a>
	inodes per table.
