ry-countlimit" title=3D"Table&nbsp;4.7.&nbsp;Indexed Directory Entry Count =
and Limit Structure">Table&nbsp;4.7, =E2=80=9CIndexed Directory Entry Count=
 and Limit Structure=E2=80=9D</a>.
    </p><p>
